ed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1014857, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "O Allah, O remover of suffering, reliever from agony, dispeller of grievances, responding to the prayers of the distressed ones, and All-beneficent and All-merciful in this world and the other world, You are beneficent to me and beneficent to all things; so, (please) have mercy upon me due to which I dispense with the mercy of any other one than You and by which You may help me settle my debts.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Ay Ma’bood! Ay andoh hata ne waale, ay gham ke dur karne waale aur ay ranj o gham ke mita ne waale, ay na-chaaro’n ki dua’e qabool karne waale, ay duniya o aakherat mein rehmat karne waale aur dono jahan mein maher-baan. Tu mujh par rehmat karne waala aur har cheez par rehmat karne waala hai, pas mujh par aisi rehmat farma keh jis se Tu mujhe apne ghair ki rehmat se be-neyaaz kar de aur uske zariye mera qarz adaa kar de.", "Urdu": "اے معبود! اے غم واندوہ ہٹانے والے اے غم کے دور کرنے والے اور اے رنج و غم کے مٹا دینے والے اے ناچاروں کی دعائیں قبول کرنے والےاے دنیا وآخرت میں رحم کرنے والے اور دونوں میں مہربان تو مجھ پر رحم کرنے والا اورہر چیز پر رحمت کرنے والا ہے پس مجھ پر ایسی رحمت عطا فرما کہ جس سے تو مجھے اپنے غیر کی رحمت سے بے نیاز کردے اور اس کے ذریعے میرا قرض ادا کردے۔", "RArabic": "ALLAAHUMMA YAA FAARE-JAL HAMME WA MO-NAFFE-SAL GHAMME WA MUZHE-BAL AH-ZAANE WA MOJEE-BA DA’WA-TIL MUZTAR-REENA YAA RAHMAA-NAD DUNYAA WAL AAKHERA-TE WA RAHEEMA-HOMAA ANTA RAHMAA-NEE WA RAHMAA-NO KULLE SHAIY-IN FAR-HAMNEE RAHMA-TAN TUGH-NEE-NEE BE-HAA A’N RAH-MATE MAN SEWAA-KA WA TAQZEE BE-HAA A’N-NID DAIY-NE.", "ArabicText1": "اَللّٰهُمَّ يَا فَارِجَ الْهَمِّ وَمُنَفِّسَ الْغَمِّ وَمُذْهِبَ الْاَحْزَانِ وَمُجِيْبَ دَعْوَةِ الْمُضْطَرِّيْنَ يَا رَحْمٰنَ الدُّنْيَا وَالْآخِرَةِ وَرَحِيْمَهُمَا اَنْتَ رَحْمٰنِىْ وَرَحْمٰنُ كُلِّ شَىْءٍ فَارْحَمْنِىْ رَحْمَةً تُغْنِيْنِىْ بِهَا عَنْ رَحْمَةِ مَنْ سِوَاكَ وَتَقْضِىْ بِهَا عَنِّى الدَّيْنَ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, 